Do you want a quote to protect your no claims discount of 8 years?

You can opt to add protected no claims discount to your policy. This means that if you make up to two fault claims within any three year period, it won't affect your no claims discount.

Please note that although this protects the level of discount you receive, it doesn't guarantee your insurance premium will stay the same.
